iv class=\"mb-2xs text-h5\">OpenAI helps Hyatt advance AI among colleagues</div>\n          <p class=\"text-meta gap-x-3xs gap-y-4xs flex flex-wrap\"><span>Global Affairs</span><span class=\"gap-x-3xs gap-y-4xs flex flex-wrap\"><time class=\"text-primary-60 text-nowrap\" datetime=\"2026-04-20T00:00\">Apr 20, 2026</time></span></p>\n         </div> \n        </a>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"mb-md relative ps-sm min-w-[calc(100%/3)] ps-0 last:me-0\">\n       <div class=\"group relative\">\n        <div class=\"ease-curve-c duration-medium max-w-container-desktop relative mx-auto w-full overflow-hidden transition-opacity rounded-md [&amp;_img]:translate-0 [&amp;_video]:translate-0 [&amp;_img]:scale-100 [&amp;_img]:transition-transform [&amp;_img]:duration-300 [&amp;_video]:transition-transform [&amp;_video]:duration-200 **:data-card-media-overlay-text:scale-100 **:data-card-media-overlay-text:transition-transform **:data-card-media-overlay-text:duration-300 group-hover:[&amp;_img]:scale-102.5 group-hover:[&amp;_video]:scale-102.5 group-hover:**:data-card-media-overlay-text:scale-102.5\">\n         <div class=\"relative w-full\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1/1\">\n          <div class=\"size-full\">\n           <div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-none -translate-inline-1/2 inset-s-1/2 top-1/2 aspect-(--image-aspect-ratio) max-h-full max-w-full -translate-y-1/2 bg-surface-loading\" style=\"--image-aspect-ratio:1/1\">\n            <img alt=\"Cloudflare OpenAI art card 1x1\" data-nosnippet=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"top:0;color:transparent;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1728px) 1728px, 100vw\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260420130344_Cloudflare_OpenAI_art_card_1x1.png 640w, https://image.jido.dev/20260420130344_Cloudflare_OpenAI_art_card_1x1.png 750w, https://image.jido.dev/20260420130344_Cloudflare_OpenAI_art_card_1x1.png 828w, https://image.jido.dev/20260420130344_Cloudflare_OpenAI_art_card_1x1.png 1080w, https://image.jido.dev/20260420130344_Cloudflare_OpenAI_art_card_1x1.png 1200w, https://image.jido.dev/20260420130344_Cloudflare_OpenAI_art_card_1x1.png 1920w, https://image.jido.dev/20260420130344_Cloudflare_OpenAI_art_card_1x1.png 2048w, https://image.jido.dev/20260420130344_Cloudflare_OpenAI_art_card_1x1.png 3840w\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260420130344_Cloudflare_OpenAI_art_card_1x1.png\">\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <a aria-label=\"Enterprises power agentic workflows in Cloudflare Agent Cloud with OpenAI - Global Affairs - Apr 13, 2026\" class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 pt-2xs duration-medium ease-curve-d block w-full transition-[opacity,background] after:absolute after:inset-0 after:content-['']\" id=\"18S371Ssqh15XWLXSydYZN\" href=\"https://openai.com/index/cloudflare-openai-agent-cloud/\"> \n         <div class=\"text-primary-100 relative w-full\">\n          <div class=\"mb-2xs text-h5\">Enterprises power agentic workflows in Cloudflare Agent Cloud with OpenAI</div>\n          <p class=\"text-meta gap-x-3xs gap-y-4xs flex flex-wrap\"><span>Global Affairs</span><span class=\"gap-x-3xs gap-y-4xs flex flex-wrap\"><time class=\"text-primary-60 text-nowrap\" datetime=\"2026-04-13T06:00\">Apr 13, 2026</time></span></p>\n         </div> \n        </a>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"mb-md relative ps-sm min-w-[calc(100%/3)] ps-0 last:me-0\">\n       <div class=\"group relative\">\n        <div class=\"ease-curve-c duration-medium max-w-container-desktop relative mx-auto w-full overflow-hidden transition-opacity rounded-md [&amp;_img]:translate-0 [&amp;_video]:translate-0 [&amp;_img]:scale-100 [&amp;_img]:transition-transform [&amp;_img]:duration-300 [&amp;_video]:transition-transform [&amp;_video]:duration-200 **:data-card-media-overlay-text:scale-100 **:data-card-media-overlay-text:transition-transform **:data-card-media-overlay-text:duration-300 group-hover:[&amp;_img]:scale-102.5 group-hover:[&amp;_video]:scale-102.5 group-hover:**:data-card-media-overlay-text:scale-102.5\">\n         <div class=\"relative w-full\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1/1\">\n          <div class=\"size-full\">\n           <div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-none -translate-inline-1/2 inset-s-1/2 top-1/2 aspect-(--image-aspect-ratio) max-h-full max-w-full -translate-y-1/2 bg-surface-loading\" style=\"--image-aspect-ratio:1/1\">\n            <img alt=\"Child safety blueprint &gt; card image\" data-nosnippet=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"top:0;color:transparent;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1728px) 1728px, 100vw\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260409220249_Frame__9_.png 640w, https://image.jido.dev/20260413130328_Frame__9_.png 750w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409220249_Frame__9_.png 828w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409220249_Frame__9_.png 1080w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409220249_Frame__9_.png 1200w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409220249_Frame__9_.png 1920w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cf02392e-9941-44e0-143e-d20f3445c500/public 2048w, https://image.jido.dev/20260409220249_Frame__9_.png 3840w\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260409220249_Frame__9_.png\">\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <a aria-label=\"Introducing the Child Safety Blueprint - Safety - Apr 8, 2026\" class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 pt-2xs duration-medium ease-curve-d block w-full transition-[opacity,background] after:absolute after:inset-0 after:content-['']\" id=\"kapCzbWVAyk44DEGUV9B0\" href=\"https://openai.com/index/introducing-child-safety-blueprint/\"> \n         <div class=\"text-primary-100 relative w-full\">\n          <div class=\"mb-2xs text-h5\">Introducing the Child Safety Blueprint</div>\n          <p class=\"text-meta gap-x-3xs gap-y-4xs flex flex-wrap\"><span>Safety</span><span class=\"gap-x-3xs gap-y-4xs flex flex-wrap\"><time class=\"text-primary-60 text-nowrap\" datetime=\"2026-04-08T05:00\">Apr 8, 2026</time></span></p>\n         </div> \n        </a>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "OpenAI 已为 ChatGPT Enterprise 和 API 平台获得 FedRAMP 20x Moderate 授权，使美国政府机构能够安全地访问 GPT-5.5 等前沿 AI 模型。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "OpenAI 已为 ChatGPT Enterprise 和 API 平台获得 FedRAMP 20x Moderate 授权，使美国政府机构能够安全地访问 GPT-5.5 等前沿 AI 模型。",
  "summary": "OpenAI 的这份官方公告详细介绍了公司为 ChatGPT Enterprise 和 API 平台获得 FedRAMP 20x Moderate 授权的成就。这一里程碑使得美国政府机构能够在符合联邦标准的安全框架内部署 OpenAI 最先进的 AI 模型，包括 GPT-5.5。文章阐述了 FedRAMP 20x 流程的重要性，该流程在不降低严谨性的前提下，提供了一条更快速、云原生的安全授权路径。文章概述了机构现在可用的能力，例如使用 ChatGPT Enterprise 进行研究、起草和分析，以及使用 API 将 AI 功能集成到现有政府系统中。公告还提供了机构与 OpenAI 接洽的实用步骤，包括通过 Carahsoft 等授权经销商进行采购，以及访问 FedRAMP Marketplace。该授权被视为让公共部门能够将尖端 AI 应用于广泛任务的关键一步，从加快审批流程到推进科学研究。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
